  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Are you nervous? Well, you shouldn't be. It's just a bunch of meat sacks,
    after all. They don't even have guns!\n\nNow to the important parts:\n- To move
    your horde, just click on the position you want them to move with the left mouse
    button.\n- To move the camera, use the WSAD-Keys or bring your cursor near the
    screen border.\n\nEasy enough, isn't it?\n\nOne thing to remember, tough, is
    that your zombie are stupid. Some of them don't even have heads!\nIf you give
    them an order to move somewhere, they will only be able to remember that command
    for a few seconds. \n\nAs long as one zombie is still following your command,
    the \"command marker\" (green cross) will be visible. If you can't place the
    marker, or it vanishes, it means that the zombies are confused or busy.\n\nIt
    is essential that you kill as many survivors as you can. Some will fight and
    some will run away. Just kill everything nearby and make sure you lose as few
    zombies as you can.\n\nHave fun killing!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5302535af1044152a457ed104f1f4b91, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2164040, guid: 5302535af1044152a457ed104f1f4b91, type: 2}
